{"type":"click","text":"FOLDERS\n          All Notes\n          Work\n          Personal\n          Recipes\n          + New Folder\n        \n        \n        \n          ALL NOTES\n          \n            Meeting Notes\n            Sprint planning discussion...\n            Today, 2:30 PM\n          \n          \n            Shopping List\n            Eggs, milk, bread...\n            Yesterday\n          \n          \n            Project Ideas\n            App improvements...\n            Mar 15\n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      A: Two-Panel (Folders + Notes List)\n      Sidebar shows folders, main area shows note previews. Clicking a note opens the editor full-width (replacing the list). Similar to Apple Notes on iPhone.\n      \n        ProsSimple and familiarWorks great on mobileMatches your existing page patterns\n        ConsCan't see notes list while editing","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1773850408171}
