{"type":"click","text":"FOLDERS\n          All Notes\n          Work\n          Personal\n          Recipes\n          + New Folder\n        \n        \n        \n          ALL NOTES\n          \n            Meeting Notes\n            Today\n          \n          \n            Shopping List\n            Yesterday\n          \n          \n            Project Ideas\n            Mar 15\n          \n        \n        \n        \n          Meeting Notes\n          Today, 2:30 PM · Work\n          \n            B\n            I\n            H1\n            ☰\n            ☑\n          \n          \n            Sprint planning discussion points:\n            • Review Q1 milestones\n            • Assign feature work\n            • Set deadlines for v2\n            Type here...\n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      B: Three-Panel (Folders + List + Editor)\n      Desktop shows all three panels at once like Apple Notes on Mac. On mobile, collapses to a drill-down navigation (folders → list → editor).\n      \n        ProsFull context at a glance on desktopQuick switching between notesTrue Apple Notes feel\n        ConsMore complex to implementRequires responsive breakpoint logic","choice":"b","id":null,"timestamp":1773850441087}
